text: Aad de Koning was a speed skater from Netherlands. Koning competed at the 1948 Winter Olympics. He was born on 25 December 1928 and died on 29 May 2010.Aad de Koning == References == Category:1928 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Dutch speed skaters Category:Olympians for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from Purmerend
